  "settings": {},
  "meta": {
    "description": "Unified SafeSite AI automation workflow combining three independent webhook-triggered branches: (1) Payroll Risk Analysis Agent at /payroll-risk-analysis-run — reuses the exact node logic from payroll-risk-analysis-agent.workflow.json, swapping its Schedule Trigger for a Webhook Trigger + immediate Respond node; (2) Safety Action Effectiveness Agent at /safety-effectiveness-run — copied verbatim from safety-effectiveness-webhook-trigger.workflow.json; (3) Real-Time Violation Alert at /safesite-violation-alert — responds 200 immediately, then normalizes and logs the violation payload (all fields treated as optional, matching backend/alerts/base.py build_alert_payload output). After import, replace placeholder values: {{BACKEND_BASE_URL}}, {{N8N_PAYROLL_AGENT_API_KEY}}, {{N8N_SAFETY_ACTION_AGENT_API_KEY}}. Activate the workflow to expose the three production webhook URLs under https://coorporate2026.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/<path>. The original three standalone workflow files (payroll-risk-analysis-agent, safety-action-effectiveness-agent, safety-effectiveness-webhook-trigger) are left untouched — keep or deactivate them per your own judgment to avoid duplicate execution."
  }
}
